VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT UseDeveloperExceptionPage\(\)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:app\.Environment\.IsProduction\(\)|ASPNETCORE_ENVIRONMENT.*Production|IsDevelopment\(\).*false && PRESENT:UseDeveloperExceptionPage\s*\(\s*\)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects developer exception middleware usage.
